<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="L" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Languish2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Languish,</orth> vb. 1) to sink and pine away: <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.1.35" default="NO" valid="yes">As II, 1, 35</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 2.3.17" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. II, 3, 17</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 3.3.43" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. III, 3, 43</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 1.1.156" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 1, 156</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 1.5.9" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 5, 9</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 1.2.31" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. I, 2, 31</bibl>. With <emph>of</emph>: <cit><quote>what is it the king --es of?</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 1.1.37" default="NO" valid="yes">All's I, 1, 37</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) to long without gratification, to pine away for love: <bibl n="shak. ven 603" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 603</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. son 145.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 145, 3</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.2.29" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. II, 2, 29</bibl>. With <emph>for</emph>: <cit><quote>l. for assured bondage,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 1.6.72" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 6, 72</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>